node.text: After a crazyyy first season @stallionaireschance  is back with an even crazier group of ladies fighting for his love!! Will he finally find the one?! Tune in to the Season 2 PREMIERE next Sunday September 19th on #Zeus! Trust me you don’t want to miss it! Subscribe now to @thezeusnetwork tune in! #ExecutiveProducer #ZeusNetwork
